50|$|TeraView has {{developed}} a number of instruments that harness the properties of <b>terahertz</b> <b>radiation.</b> Terahertz light has some interesting application. Many common materials and living tissues are semi-transparent and have ‘terahertz fingerprints’, permitting them to be imaged, identified, and analyzed. Moreover, the non-ionizing properties of <b>terahertz</b> <b>radiation</b> and the relatively low power levels used, indicate that it is safe.|$|E
